Instance Constructors

  1. new AutoContrast(saturated: Double, normalize: Boolean = false)

    saturated

    percentile saturation. Clamps outliers outside saturation bounds to the min max saturation value. This keeps autocontrast from using extremely outliers as the min/max.

    normalize

    if true then it Stretches the pixels between min and max values. Otherwise it clamps values.
